y predicted to\noccur in this compound, and suggest that BFO can be viewed as a polytypic\nmaterial. Our work thus contributes to shape a coherent picture of the\nstructural variants that BFO can present and the way in which they are related.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2012 19:18:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
