 flat spectrum sources are a result of the cores of FRI sources becoming\ndominant at high frequencies. These results highlight the importance of\nstudying this faint, high frequency population.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Nov 2012 14:57:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-06"}
